data.description:
You'll like what you see when you step inside - The front entry brings you into the living room with a cathedral ceiling and fireplace. Then the dining area shares space with the kitchen that's outfitted with SS appliances, granite counters and lots of cabinets. The living room is spacious and bright. The Primary Bedroom has its private bath with a nicely tiled shower.
In addition to the 2 secondary bedrooms the BONUS ROOM can be the 4th bedroom you need or the office space you want. The home also has a single car garage and parking pad and a spacious back yard.  See the picture gallery for info!
